<L>Of his lyf he was a-nuy&yogh;ed&middot; he wilnede to ben of dawe:</L>
<L>He sat&middot; and Carede of his lyf&middot;: he clepte his sone Seth:<MILESTONE N="29:1" UNIT="folio"></L>
<L N="36">"Leoue sone&middot; icham weri of-liued&middot;, ich wilne aftur my de&thorn;:</L>
